snippet.title: A Very Honest Body Language Review Of Amber Heard's & Johnny Depp's Hearings
snippet.description:
Hello my dearest Talkers, and welcome back to another video for today.
This time, I've taken my lifetime experience with people, and behavior, in order to try and understand what does one person show in a official court hearing. Therefore I've watched the hearing of Amber Heard & Johnny Depp.
If You have any advise, or more information I should know, please let me know, and I'll be happy connecting with you all!!

My IG is: somoditomer27.

Take care Talkers, and stay safe!!

#AmberHeardHearing #JohhnyDeppCourtCase
